para.latex:
\begin{eqnarray}
f(x,a,b) =
\left\{
\begin{array}{l}
0, \textrm{ if } x< a, \\
\frac{1}{b-a}, \textrm{ if } x\in[a,b], \\
1, \textrm{ if } x> b.
\end{array}
\right.
\end{eqnarray}

